snippet.title: Aristotle Deep Thought Quotes #shorts
snippet.description:
Aristotle Deep Thought Quotes #shorts

Aristotle was a Greek philosopher and polymath during the Classical period in Ancient Greece. Taught by Plato, he was the founder of the Lyceum, the Peripatetic school of philosophy, and the Aristotelian tradition.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Aristotle. The best quotes and aphorisms of Aristotle that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Aristotle are definitely worth your time.

Thank you for watching!
